  Bar Code Example :

  \;

  <\fish-code>
    fish define calc_stress(depth, gamma)

    \ \ \ \ local pore = 9810.0 * depth

    \ \ \ \ local total = gamma * depth

    \ \ \ \ local eff = total - pore

    \ \ \ \ io.out('Force:' + string(eff) + ' Pa')

    \ \ \ \ calc_stress = eff

    end
  </fish-code>

